<item>
            <title>[LU-12646] Restore performance enhancement from  LU-11413</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12646</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11413&quot; title=&quot;Large performance degradation in routing environment. &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11413&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11413&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; modified the behavior of route selection for GET REPLY and PUT ACK by making it so that we use the same router where the GET/PUT arrived from. This enhancement was lost in the MR-Routing feature that has landed for 2.13. This ticket is to track restoring this behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
